### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### List all categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?page=1&pageSize=20
Content-Type: application/json

### Search categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?q=electronics&page=1&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Get child categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?parentSlug=electronics&page=1&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Get category by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/CATEGORY_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Get category by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/slug/electronics
Content-Type: application/json

### Create new category (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics",
  "slug": "electronics",
  "description": "Electronic devices and accessories"
}

### Create child category (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptops",
  "slug": "laptops",
  "description": "Laptop computers",
  "parentId": "PARENT_CATEGORY_ID_HERE"
}

### Update category (admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/categories/CATEGORY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics & Gadgets",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Delete category (admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/CATEGORY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}